Product Description               Designed by parents, for parents, this extra wide baby safety gate from Regalo helps create a safer home for babies, toddlers, and pets. American designed and American owned, Regalo is a family-owned, U.S.-based brand that has delivered trusted child safety products for over 30 years. This tested and trusted baby gate is certified by the Baby Safety Alliance and has been relied on by parents for decades to help protect children in everyday home environments. Built with durability and ease of use in mind, this safety gate provides dependable protection without sacrificing convenience. The extra wide safety gate for doorways and bottom of stairs adjusts to fit openings 29 to 56 inches wide and stands 30 inches tall. Designed for simple setup, installs according to the manufacturer’s instructions. Wall cups must be used to keep the gate securely in place. ⚠️ To help prevent falls, this gate should never be used at the top of stairs. This child and pet safety gate features a convenient walk-through door with a secure safety locking system, making it easy for adults to pass through while helping keep babies safe. Ideal for children 6–24 months and small to medium pets, this gate works well as both a baby gate and pet gate. Puerta de seguridad para bebés y mascotas — esta puerta de seguridad es ideal para bebés de 6 a 24 meses y mascotas pequeñas a medianas. Su diseño práctico con puerta abatible y sistema de cierre seguro ofrece comodidad para los padres y tranquilidad en el hogar. Whether you’re securing doorways or creating safe boundaries inside your home, this Regalo baby safety gate delivers reliable protection, thoughtful design, and trusted quality from a brand parents have depended on for generations.                  Brand Story               By               
