                    From the Manufacturer               Wide or narrow openings this one fits them ALL. Introducing the Regalo Extra Wide WIDESPAN safety gate. This sturdy, all metal walk-thru gate accommodates a variety of openings ranging from 29 inches to 56 inches. No need to purchase extra extensions this gate includes a 4, 8, and 12 extension kits. Gate height is 30 inches. The easy to adjust pressure mounting system makes installation quick and easy. When your hands are full the convenient one-hand walk thru design makes your job a little easier. The Regalo WIDESPAN meets all current safety standards. Great for pets too. You will notice a slight gap between the gate door latch and the frame. This is not a defect. Your gate is a pressure mounted gate and this gap will disappear once you tighten your gate in its opening.             See more
